  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1010">
<l>cīruṭaic celvar ciṟutuṉi māri </l>
<l>vaṟaṅkūrn taṉaiya tuṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The short-lived poverty of those who are noble and rich is like the clouds becoming poor (for a while).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
